data.description: Welcome to this beautiful 2 story colonial home that we all have passed by as it sits back on slightly over 2 acres of land that is zoned commercial in Cheektowaga. You have 3 different entrances into your new home. Walk through the front door into your foyer, and enjoy the comfort of your spacious first floor home. There you will find your living room with a gas fireplace, formal dining room, a eat in kitchen, a office space, a half bath and across the way a shower as well. On the 2nd floor you have your bedrooms and a full bath with a separate shower with 4 shower heads and a jacuzzi tub. From the 2nd floor landing you have an open space that leads to a rear top porch that over looks your rear yard. There are laundry hookups on the 2nd floor as well as an additional set in the basement. In the basement you will find another full bath and 2 finished off office spaces. In the rear of the basement there is plenty of storage space or can be used for a workshop. There is updated electric, a tankless hot water tank, central air and more.
